es.eucm.eadandroid.common.loader
Interface InputStreamCreator

All Known Implementing Classes:
ResourceHandler, ResourceHandlerExternalSource, ResourceHandlerRestricted, ResourceHandlerUnrestricted
public interface InputStreamCreator

Constructs the InputStream of a file located in a parent structure, which is abstracted by this entity . Entities aiming to use Loader must implement this interface
